Bitten centers on Elena Michaels, the world's only female werewolf who, years after being bitten, is working as a journalist in Toronto and trying to keep mum about her secret. She's forced to confront her past, though, when a bunch of bodies turn up at a werewolf sanctuary. Based off the "Otherworld" book series by Kelley Armstrong.
